<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services- DriveHub</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.jpg">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 7px 0; /* Decrease header padding */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .header a:hover {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .header-text {
            text-align: left;
            width: 70%; /* Set the width of the header text */
            max-width: 600px; /* Max width of the header text */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center the header text */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px; /* Increase the size of the box */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .service {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <a href="/register_login"> <img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="Company Logo" class="logo" height="50px" width="150px"></a>
        <div class="header-text">
            <h1>Welcome to DriveHub</h1>
            <p>Your premier destination for online vehicle rentals</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>SERVICES</h2>
            <p>Services That Drive Hub Offers:</p>
            <div class="service">
                1. Vast Fleet of Vehicles: Drive Hub provides a large selection of cars and bikes to suit a variety of tastes and requirements, including sedans, SUVs, small cars, motorbikes, and more.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                2. Online Booking: Drive Hub's user-friendly website makes it simple for customers to reserve the vehicle of their choice from any location at any time.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                3. Adaptable Rental Options: Drive Hub offers a range of rental times, so clients can select the period that best fits their schedules, from a few hours to several days.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                4. Self-Drive Experience: Drive Hub is an expert in self-drive rentals, giving clients the liberty and adaptability to see places at their own speed.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                5. Clear Pricing: Drive Hub makes sure that there are no unanticipated costs or hidden charges, so clients can budget with confidence for their rental.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                6. Vehicle Customization: Depending on their tastes, customers can choose particular amenities and features for their vehicles, making their driving experiences unique.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                7. Comprehensive Insurance Coverage: Drive Hub offers a range of options for comprehensive insurance coverage, giving clients security and comfort throughout their rental experience.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                8. 24/7 Customer Support: Drive Hub's committed customer service team is on hand to help clients with any questions, bookings, or support they may require.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                9. Vehicle Maintenance and Inspection: To guarantee every rental vehicle is safe and dependable, Drive Hub performs comprehensive inspections and routine maintenance on its fleet.
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                10. Convenient Pickup and Drop-off: Drive Hub makes it simple for clients to pick up and return their rental vehicles at the locations of their choice by providing convenient pickup and drop-off locations.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 DriveHub. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>